Invocation Name: super heroes
des:
This skill is designed to engage superhero fans of all ages by telling a motivational quote or an interesting facts about super heroes.

To get started, try saying: "Alexa, ask Super Heroes for a quote.", "Alexa, ask Super Heroes to Inspire me.", "Alexa, ask Super Heroes to Motivate me.", "Alexa, ask Super Heroes for a fact.", "Alexa, ask Super Heroes for trivia."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
